data.description:
Welcome to Mission Royale, a 55+ lifestyle community! This stunning 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers a split floor plan and a spacious open layout that's perfect for comfortable living. With modern amenities and numerous upgrades. Including New A/C Unit, Outlets added in great room & Covered patio. 
Freshly Painted and Tile in every room. Large owner's suite bathroom and walk-in closet. Eat in kitchen with a breakfast bar for quick meals. Owned water softener, newer water heater. 2 car garage with built in cabinets. Covered Patio and plenty of shade. Backyard has lemon and fruit trees with fruit. Plants well manicured. Truly one of a kind find in Casa Grande. Close to Restaurants and the Promenade Shopping Center.
